videos.headline: WMU gets the turnover when QB forgets to throw the ball
videos.description: Ohio quarterback Quinton Maxwell has the ball slip out of his hand trying to throw the quick out pass and Western Michigan falls on it for the first turnover of the game.

videos.headline: WMU recovers Ohio fumble on kickoff
videos.description: Derrick Mitchell kickoff for 65 yds , Kyle Belack return for 17 yds to the Ohio 17 Kyle Belack fumbled, forced by Trevor Sweeney, recovered by WMich Giovanni Ricci

videos.headline: G. Windham pass to P. White for 67 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Greg Windham pass complete to Papi White for 67 yds to the WMich 6 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Ohio strikes back with 8-yard TD pass
videos.description: Ohio isn't going away quietly in the MAC championship game as Greg Windham hits Jordan Reid on the slant pass for an 8-yard touchdown to cut into Western Michigan's lead at 9-7.

videos.headline: No one's catching Davis for WMU 70-yard touchdown
videos.description: Corey Davis makes the catch, breaks through a tackle and is gone for a 70-yard touchdown strike to boost Western Michigan's lead to 16-7.

videos.headline: Western Michigan finds end zone just before halftime
videos.description: Western Michigan's Zach Terrell scrambles right and rather than go out of bounds he finds Carrington Thompson in the end zone for a Broncos' touchdown with 36 seconds left in the half.

videos.headline: Tipped pass leads to interception by Ohio
videos.description: Zach Terrell pass intercepted Bradd Ellis return for 42 yds to the WMich 5

videos.headline: Reed's second TD gets Ohio back in the game
videos.description: After an interception set Ohio up deep in Western Michigan territory, Jordan Reed hauls in the pass from five yards out to get the Bobcats back to within 10 at 23-13.

videos.headline: Ohio strikes again with White 31-yard TD
videos.description: Ohio continues to hang around in the MAC championship game when Greg Windham goes deep to Papi White for a 31-yard touchdown to pull the Bobcats to within six of Western Michigan.

videos.headline: Z. Terrell pass intercepted by K. Nelson
videos.description: Zach Terrell pass intercepted Kylan Nelson return for no gain to the Ohio 32

videos.headline: Late interception wins Western Michigan the MAC title
videos.description: Trailing by six and driving with under a minute to go, Ohio quarterback Greg Windham throws a pick to kill the drive and seal the MAC championship for Western Michigan.

videos.headline: Fleck adamant Western Michigan is going to Cotton Bowl
videos.description: P.J. Fleck makes it clear his mind is set on Western Michigan making the Cotton Bowl and says the Broncos are the best Group of 5 team in the country.
